data.description: $5,000 towards the buyer's closing cost!!! Welcome to your dream home at 13510 Ailey Knoll, a captivating residence in the heart of San Antonio, TX 78254. This stunning property offers an exquisite blend of modern luxury and timeless charm, making it the perfect place to call home.    With a spacious and well-designed floor plan, this home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for your family to grow and thrive. The master suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a private ensuite bathroom and a generously sized walk-in closet.    Step into the heart of the home, a beautifully appointed kitchen with modern appliances, sleek countertops, and an abundance of storage space. The kitchen flows seamlessly into the open-concept living and dining areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends and family.    One of the many highlights of this property is the beautiful design, which offers coziness and warmth. This space is ideal for anyone.    The outdoor area is equally impressive, featuring a covered patio and an easy-maintenance backyard. It's the perfect spot for enjoying San Antonio's beautiful weather, hosting barbecues, or simply unwinding after a long day.    This home is located in a vibrant community and offers easy access to gorgeous amenities like a pool, water slide, catch and release pond, and basketball, volleyball, and sports courts; close by located schools, parks, shopping centers, and Lackland AFB.    This is the one if you're looking for a property that combines comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make 13510 Ailey Knoll your new home sweet home.
